body_html: @junshi15 This issue is not caused by PR#8934, but an error in grpc_call.h which should include refcount.h. However, refcount.h was luckly included before grpc_call.h in grpc_verbs_service target (and also other targets). And there should a recent change which removed this indirect include which leads to this compile error.

body: @junshi15 This issue is not caused by PR#8934, but an error in `grpc_call.h` which should include `refcount.h`. However, `refcount.h` was luckly included before `grpc_call.h` in `grpc_verbs_service` target (and also other targets). And there should a recent change which removed this indirect include which leads to this compile error.
